item.title: Masters of the Universe (Binary Star album)
item.description: Masters of the Universe is the second and final studio album from American hip hop duo Binary Star (Senim Silla & One Be Lo), released on October 31, 2000. The release is largely a remixed and rearranged version of their 1999 debut Waterworld. The album was one of the most acclaimed underground hip hop releases of 2000, though it only sold around 20,000 copies. Masters of the Universe was re-released on July 25, 2006 by Infinite Rhythm Network.
